{"tid":158941,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"香港月租酒店邊間平","createTime":"2017-03-16T15:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T16:32:32.000Z","uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2db96b70724d2110b57f368a859736d3861908","tid":158941,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:34:52.000Z","msg":"黎緊4月尾想租地方住 想問下如果酒店邊間平？"},{"pid":"c04e8485a0637d10541b6eddd6dab5e934aa64b7","tid":158941,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2afb9f12ee98eb9554c12b3fa999cf90725aac","tid":158941,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9178500114dfc00a00663d38ab9a104610f96f72","tid":158941,"uid":62443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:27:50.000Z","msg":"露宿者之家"},{"pid":"9e363404b3d3274469ad3d779108a02741672654","tid":158941,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:17:35.000Z","msg":"嘉湖海逸酒店有月租PLAN<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://archive.am730.com.hk/article-314928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.am730.com.hk%2Farticle-314928&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d9b00d56\" target=\"_blank\">http://archive.am730.com.hk/article-314928</a>"},{"pid":"8f576c38e1652722ec8aba4b65c398b2532e8357","tid":158941,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:19:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.edigest.hk/property_market/香港酒店劈價-日租平過劏房/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2Fproperty_market%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E5%8A%88%E5%83%B9-%E6%97%A5%E7%A7%9F%E5%B9%B3%E9%81%8E%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%2F&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=81b6d1aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.edigest.hk/property_market/香港酒店劈價-日租平過劏房/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.edigest.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/57e3b8a3eb09d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.edigest.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F57e3b8a3eb09d.jpg&h=81020a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年訪港旅客減少，十一黃金週前夕，本地酒店出現劈價潮，部分更平至一晚200元有交易！酒店房間一般有150呎，有人幫手執房、水電煤全包，部分更免費使用設施，住一個隨時比住劏房更抵！<br />\n<br />\n撰文：Nic Chan<br />\n<br />\n小編以9月27至28日（星期二、三）作標準，淨房以兩人房的價錢計算，有9間3星級酒店，一晚只需300元以下，其中6間更是市區酒店。<br />\n<br />\n以最平的青衣盛逸酒店為例，一晚只需186元，住足一個月只需5,580元，據酒店網站介紹，其設有200米露天泳池、桑拿、健身室等設施。而同區的華逸酒店，一晚要292元，一個月亦只需8,760元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.edigest.hk/wp-content/uploads/articles/articlecelebrity_920x483_0/4910/57e3b8a433149_1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.edigest.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Farticles%2Farticlecelebrity_920x483_0%2F4910%2F57e3b8a433149_1.png&h=dcc7a1d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據早前媒體報導，一個土瓜灣120呎劏房的月租要5,300元、灣仔185呎劏房更要7,800元，除開日租分別要176元及260元。相比之下，紅磡的紅茶館酒店（紅磡溫思路街）日租僅230元，灣仔的雅逸酒店亦只是289元，可見目前酒店價格確實平得可憐。大家同樣百幾呎空間，價錢又差不多，做乜要咁慘住劏房？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.edigest.hk/wp-content/uploads/articles/articlecelebrity_920x483_0/4910/57e3b8a4699cd_1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.edigest.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Farticles%2Farticlecelebrity_920x483_0%2F4910%2F57e3b8a4699cd_1.png&h=79581a33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f2ed51349afb37fb4154b537109cd8948ec5e83","tid":158941,"uid":90422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘉湖海逸酒店有月租PLAN<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://archive.am730.com.hk/article-314928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.am730.com.hk%2Farticle-314928&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d9b00d56\" target=\"_blank\">http://archive.am730.com.hk/article-314928</a></blockquote><br />\n萬3蚊我租我間房比你算啦 3000蚊包水電媒包wifi<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f9203885732316c9c3ee2293ea03feb4d5ef04","tid":158941,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嘉湖海逸酒店有月租PLAN<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://archive.am730.com.hk/article-314928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.am730.com.hk%2Farticle-314928&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d9b00d56\" target=\"_blank\">http://archive.am730.com.hk/article-314928</a></blockquote><br />\n萬3蚊我租我間房比你算啦 3000蚊包水電媒包wifi<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你影你間房出黎比較下<br />\n<br />\n有無會所用?"}]}